
###############################
Please execute the following orders
1) open in Browser
https://github.com/cmetzig/MelodyFeatures

2) click green button that says code, the window that opens has the option 'DownloaD ZIP' at the bottom, select that and download it
save in a directory (example: melody_dir) and unzip. It should generate a folder called MelodyFeatures-master.

3) open Rstudio
set the working directory by clicking Session -> Set Working Directory -> Choose Directory  -> melody_dir
(this path should now appear in the top line of the console)

4) type in the console the following comments, followed by enter

install.packages("devtools")
install.packages("tuneR")
library(devtools)
library(tuneR)
install_local("MelodyFeatures-master/MelodyFeatures_1.0/MelodyFeatures")


or, if it is the second attempt
install_local("MelodyFeatures-master/MelodyFeatures_1.0/MelodyFeatures", force=TRUE)


if the word DONE appears at the end, you were successful!
